    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过紧张刺激的街机式游戏操控与美妙绝伦的像素美术风格，体验《终结者2：审判日》的剧情！扮演莎拉·康纳与T-800，完成一系列扣人心弦的任务，与T-1000展开较量，阻止天网对人类的清除计划。扮演约翰·康纳，率领未来世界的反抗军，并作为人类的仅存希望，在与机器作战的前线奋勇拼杀。本作将《终结者2：审判日》中广为人知的电影场景与原创游戏场景和多重结局融为一炉，为你讲述一个独一无二的故事，让你来决定人类命运的走向。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一段经典的街机游戏之旅，畅享我们为致敬《终结者》世界而全新打造的原汁原味的街机游戏体验、音乐与视觉效果。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/10efb11641767fa5bac773ab214257b2.avif?t=1770046700\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras_big/10efb11641767fa5bac773ab214257b2.avif?t=1770046700 width=800 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重温那些“名场面”，扮演莎拉、约翰以及T-800，在融合了《终结者2：审判日》经典场景与其他不为人知的终结者故事的冒险中开拓全新旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/cc12f824ccedf6ea0b0515f2a3ea9120.poster.avif?t=1770046700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/cc12f824ccedf6ea0b0515f2a3ea9120.webm?t=1770046700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/cc12f824ccedf6ea0b0515f2a3ea9120.mp4?t=1770046700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/61d62afb31a8567dc36b8cc6ccc85340.avif?t=1770046700\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras_big/61d62afb31a8567dc36b8cc6ccc85340.avif?t=1770046700 width=800 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与实力强大、武器众多的塞伯坦企业和天网展开战斗，迎击多种类型的敌人，进行令人肾上腺素狂飙的首领战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在五花八门的关卡中射击、潜行并躲避T-1000的利刃；扮演约翰·康纳，在关键的未来战争任务中率领反抗军。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/23bc08184446da159266c2d21ef58dfe.poster.avif?t=1770046700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/23bc08184446da159266c2d21ef58dfe.webm?t=1770046700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/23bc08184446da159266c2d21ef58dfe.mp4?t=1770046700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/9b291a0308505bb35ec804f465a141a7.avif?t=1770046700\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras_big/9b291a0308505bb35ec804f465a141a7.avif?t=1770046700 width=800 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个关卡中都尽力获得最高排名，称霸高分排行榜，铸就不朽的街机传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/f10b147e72dc33b070d5bda6e7dfb3c8.poster.avif?t=1770046700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/f10b147e72dc33b070d5bda6e7dfb3c8.webm?t=1770046700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/f10b147e72dc33b070d5bda6e7dfb3c8.mp4?t=1770046700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/6f635f42b569cee9c8e95fef7699241f.avif?t=1770046700\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras_big/6f635f42b569cee9c8e95fef7699241f.avif?t=1770046700 width=800 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聆听比肩电影原声大碟的游戏音乐，包含重制版的《终结者2：审判日》音乐以及全新曲目。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras/b671869bc4bc011ddd4bf47b158fc2f5.avif?t=1770046700\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718460/extras_big/b671869bc4bc011ddd4bf47b158fc2f5.avif?t=1770046700 width=800 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更有多种不同游戏模式等你来挑战：故事模式、街机模式、无限模式、首领突袭、未来之母以及关卡训练！</p>",
